headline: AI boom will continue despite bubble fears: Arm CMO

headline: Tesla Stock Rises. ‘Who Would Not Want Their Own Personal R2-D2?’

Before the bump, on Friday, CEO Elon Musk spoke with Ron Baron, his “true and tested friend,” as well as a longtime Tesla and SpaceX shareholder, at the annual Baron Capital Investment Conference.  “Ultimately [there will] be billions of humanoid robots,” said Musk early in the hourlong interview.
